comment: Nurkic (DEN) clears and is not in the lane without actively guarding for more than three seconds.

Nurkic (DEN) dislodges Valanciunas (TOR) and affects his movement to the rebound. Carroll (TOR) also holds Nurkic's arm and affects his movement to the rebound, but Valanciunas maintains legal guarding position on Nurkicâ€™s put-back shot attempt.
Gallinari (DEN) maintains legal guarding position and does not make body contact that affects Lowry's (TOR) movement to the basket.
DeRozan (TOR) holds Chandler (DEN) around the waist and affects his FOM on the inbound.
Nurkic (DEN) sets the screen on Carroll (TOR) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
[Detectable with stop watch] Valanciunas (TOR) is in the paint for longer than three seconds.
Lowry (TOR) keeps his left pivot foot planted before going up for the shot.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that time had expired was overturned. Denver was given possession.
